frames.caption: A majestic phoenix rises against a dark, starry backdrop, its fiery plumage illuminating the scene. The vibrant orange and yellow flames of its wings and tail create a striking contrast with the night sky. The mythical bird appears to be in motion, symbolizing rebirth and renewal.
